snippet.title: CyberKongz X Evaverse Collab
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Evaverse! We've got fun and games!

CyberKongz is one of the biggest NFTs out there and we’re super honored to partner with them. Kongz X Eva together strong !ooh

Connect your wallet to your Evaverse account and get one of three random CyberKongz avatars to peel out on! See you in the Evaverse!
